{"questionId":"3097003","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let the volume of this barrel be <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi><mo> </mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Show that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>(</mo><msup><mi>d</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>h</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>h</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>)</mo></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>h</mi><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>(</mo><msup><mi>d</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>h</mi><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> The <em><strong>M1</strong></em> is for the substitution of their expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math> into their formula for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi></math>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>(</mo><msup><mi>d</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>h</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>h</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>AG</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"3097003","referenceCode":"23M.3.AHL.TZ1.1d","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title